            <p class="text-center">Ever since Aleks has taken over the buisness he has shifted from supplying other companies and focuses more on the wholesale and catering aspect of the buisness. With a much larger push in marketing and producing hot, ready to eat food. Adding Sasha and Aleksandra to the team has only broadened the potential reach of the buisness, allowing more people access to more authentic foods. In October 2021 Lazic Deli was hired to cater a wedding of about 500 people, the team seen in the picture on the right were all present preparing food from 9am to 1am. Since then, Harczaks has continued to expand into the world of catering and hot food. Feel free to call or <a href="/contact">contact us</a> for any catering inquiries! </p>
